    {
      "instruction": "<p>Rinse the <strong>puy-style&nbsp;lentils</strong> in a sieve under cold running water</p>\r\n<p>Once rinsed,&nbsp;add them to a medium pot with 500ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1L]</span><strong>&nbsp;cold water</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 20-25 min or until tender</p>\r\n<p>Once tender, drain and set aside</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
