    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>cauliflower</strong> from the stem into bite-sized pieces and add them to a baking tray&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Drizzle the <strong>cauliflower</strong> with <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for 20 min or until the cauliflower is golden and crisp</p>",
